longBusinessSummary: Hanstone Gold Corp. engages in the acquisition and exploration of mineral properties. It holds interest Doc Property that comprise 8 mineral claims located in the Skeena Mining Division in British Columbia; and Snip North Property, which include 5 mineral claims located in British Columbia. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
